This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with text classification and natural language processing. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of deep learning models for text classification. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as text classification is a common task in information retrieval. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks for text classification.
